Kim-ku3: Lian5 gin2-na2 ti7 sou2 choe3 e5, ia7 hian2-beng5 i e5 pun2-seng3. (Chim-gian5 20:11)
Ti7 A-hui-li7-ka e5 bou2 chit8 sou2-chai7. U7 chit8-jit8 chit8 e5 phah-lah8--e5 ti7 chhiu7-na5 lai7 chhoe7-khoann3 u7 sim2-mih8 khim5-siu3 thang liah8 bo5. Hut-jian5 tu2-tioh8 chit8 e5 chhim-chhim e5 ham7-khinn, oa2-khi3 khoann3-mai7, ti7 hit lai7-bin7 u7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2, chit8-chiah pa3, chit8-chiah niau2-chhi2, chit8-boe2 tok8-choa5, in si7 poah8-loh8 chit e5 ham7-khinn boe7 tit khi2-lai5 e5. In khoann3-kinn3 chit e5 phah-lah8 e5 chiu7 au5-kio3 kong2, “Kho2-lin5 kiu3 goan2 khi2-lai5 ah.” Hit e5 phah-lah8 e5 sui5-si5 kiu3 hit e5 gin2-na2 khi2-lai5. Chong2-si7 tui3 pa3 kong2, “Li2 siong5-siong5 thau ka7 goan2 e5 iunn5-a2 goa2 m7 kiu3 li2.” Tui3 choa5 kong2, “Li2 siong5-siong5 ai3 ka7 lang5 goa2 ia7 m7 kiu3 li2.” Tui3 niau2-chhi2 kong2, “Li2 ai3 thau chiah8 lang5 e5 mih8 m7 kiu3 li2 chhut-lai5.” Chit 3 chiah tong7-but8 tui3 an2-ni lau5 bak8-sai2 ai-kiu5, “Chhiann2 li2 kho2-lin5 goan2, li2 na7 kiu3 goan2, goan2 au7-lai5 tek-khak oe7 po3-tap li2 e5 un.” Tui3 an2-ni i long2 ka7 in kiu3 khi2-lai5, tai7-ke ka7 i seh-sia7 cho3 in khi3. Chong2-si7 chit e5 gin2-na2 bo5 chhu3 thang to3-khi3, chit e5 ho2-sim e5 lah8-jin5 chiu7 chhoa7 i khi3 in chhu3 toa3.
Koe3 bo5 joa7-ku2 hit-chiah choa5 theh8 chit8-pau e5 ioh8-a2 lai5 sang3 chit e5 lah8-jin5, kong2, “Bo5-lun7 sim2-mih8 tok8-choa5 ka7 tioh8 ka7 i boah tiam3 khang-chhui3 tek-khak oe7 ho2, goa2 eng7 che ka7 li2 tap-sia7.” I chiu7 siu khi2-lai5 toa3 ti7 i e5 sin-khu. Hit chiah pa3 ia7 tak8 cha2-khi2 ka7 lok8-a2 a2-si7 thou3-a2, a2-si7 pat8-hang7 e5 cheng-sinn lai5 hou7 in chiah8. Tui3 an2-ni chit e5 lah8-jin5 m7-bian2 koh chhut-khi3 phah-lah8, hit e5 gin2-na2 ia7 kap i sann-kap hiong2-siu7. Koe3 bo5 joa7-ku2 hit-chiah niau2-chhi2 ka7 chit8-te7 e5 pou3-te7 lai5 sang3 hit e5 lang5 kong2: “Chit lai7-bin7 u7 kim-gun5 po2-poe3 chhiann2 li2 siu khi2-lai5 thang hiong2-siu7.” I khui khoann3-mai7 ko2-jian5 lai7-bin7 long2 si7 chin tat8-chinn5 e5 mih8. I chiu7 boe7 tam7-poh8 khi2 sin-chhu3, boe2 sin-sann pinn3-cho3 chin ho2-giah8 e5 lang5. Hit e5 gin2-na2 ia7 ti7 hia hou7 i ho2 khoan2-thai7, m7-na7 bo5 kam2-sia7 hit e5 lang5 kiu3 i, hoan2-tng2 khi2 phainn2-sim siunn7 beh hai7 hit e5 lang5, thang tit-tioh8 i e5 po2-poe3.
U7 chit8-jit8 chit e5 gin2-na2 thiann-tioh8 ong5 e5 ko3-si7 kong2: “Na7 u7 lang5 liah8-tioh8 a2-si7 lai5 po3 thau-theh8 ong5-kiong e5 po2-mih8 e5 beh chiong hiah e5 po2-mih8 e5 chit8-poann3 siunn2 i.” Chit e5 gin2-na2 siunn7 kong2 si7 chin ho2 e5 ki-hoe7 chiu7 khi3 po3, kio3 kui2-na7 e5 peng-a2 lai5 liah8 chit e5 lah8-jin5 khi3. Ong5 chin siu7-khi3 sui5-si5 beng7-leng7 keh-jit8 tioh8 ka7 i chhu2 si2-heng5. Tann tu2-tu2 beh si2-heng5 e5 si5, u7 thiann kong2 ong5-chu2 hou7 choa5 ka7-tioh8 tit beh si2, chit e5 lang5 thiann-tioh8 chiu7 kong2 i u7 chin ho2 e5 ioh8-a2 tek-khak oe7 ho2, chiu7 theh8 tok8-choa5 hou7 i e5 ioh8-a2 khi2-lai5, hou7 ong5-chu2 chhi3-kou5. Kou5 liau2 ko2-jian5 ho2, ong5 chiu7 sia3-bian2 i bo5 choe7, au7-lai5 tiau-cha liau2 chiah chai hiah e5 po2-poe3 m7 si7 i thau-theh8 e5, si7 chhat8-a2 thau-theh8 chhut-lai5 chhang3 ti7 chhiu7-na5 lai7 e5, hou7 niau2-chhi2 thoa-khi3 sang3 hit e5 lah8-jin5 e5. Na7-si7 hit e5 phainn2-sim gin2-na2, ong5 beng7-leng7 liah8-khi3 koainn-kann ka7 i heng5-hoat8.
